branchCategory.name: CS2, Double Acting, Single Rod, Temperature Options
branchCategory.description: <P>Series CS2 with high temperature option is a double acting, single rod, non-lube air cylinder. Aluminum die-cast is used for both the rod and head covers, which keep the actuator light weight. This series is available in bore sizes 125mm, 140mm, and 160mm.</P>
